<br />
<blockquote><b>Quote:</b><br><span class="quote">...level 18 bard...</span></blockquote>
<br />

<br />
How did you fear kite at level 18, when snare is level 23 and fear is level 26?
<br />

<br />
no offense...
<br />

<br />
But with that said, I would say it illustrates an important fact.  
<br />

<br />
Levels 18 thru 27 and onward to level 30 and 39 are INCREDIBLY changing times for a bard.  There are a ton of tactics coming available to you in just a few levels, AOE tanking... slowing.. snaring... fear kiting... charm kiting... better mezzing ability... chants making kiting more efficient... improving group utility.. etc.   There is so much to do and learn in so short a time... approach it right and that is an incredibly fun and educational time to be a bard.</span></td>
